;
;
L00,Brake Electronics (J104/Bosch 5.7) Login
L01,0?xxx: Chassis
L02,5 = VW Phaeton (3D)
L03,0x?xx: Brakes
L04,1 = Brembo 18" (PR-1LC)
L05,2 = HP2 16" (PR-1LX)
L06,4 = 2FNR 42 AL 17" (PR-1ZL/1ZK)
L07,0xx?x: Engine
L08,4 = 10 Cyl. Diesel Engine (PR-T2M)
L09,5 = 6 Cyl. Diesel Engine (PR-T41)
L10,6 = 6 Cyl. Gasoline Engine (PR-T31) with All-Wheel-Drive (AWD)
L11,7 = 8 Cyl. Gasoline Engine (PR-T81)
L12,9 = 6 Cyl. Gasoline Engine (PR-T31) with Front-Wheel-Drive (FWD)
L13,9 = 12 Cyl. Gasoline Engine (PR-T08/T1H)
L14,0xxx?: Transmission
L15,5 = Manual Transmission (01E - PR-G0K)
L16,7 = Automatic Transmission (01L/01V - PR-G0F/G0Q)
L17,6 = Automatic Transmission (09L - PR-G0R)
L18, 
L19,Note: After Login/Coding-II has been carried out you need to recode the Control Module.
L20, 
L21,40168 = Basic Settings Enabling (i.e. mandatory prior to Steering Angle Sensor Alignment)
;
